flowchart TD
  Action[User action] --> Surface[Frontend surface]
  Surface --> Service[Client service]
  Service --> Edge[Edge function]
  Edge --> Route{Canonical ai-route?}
  Route -->|yes| AIRoute[ai-route]
  Route -->|dedicated exception| Exception[Dedicated route]
  Exception --> AIRoute
  Exception --> ProviderDirect[Provider direct path]
  AIRoute --> Auth[Auth / admin bypass / tier resolution]
  Auth --> Flags[Feature flags and route keys]
  Flags --> Limits[Daily limits / usage configs]
  Limits --> Debit[Credit debit / reserve]
  Debit --> Keys[Admin key pool / tier defaults / model routes]
  Keys --> Provider[AI Provider]
  Provider --> Fallback[Fallback / retry / structured failure]
  Fallback --> Refund[Refund when needed]
  Refund --> Logs[ai_route_events / usage_events / admin_audit_log]
  Logs --> Admin[Admin AI Systems Map]
  Logs --> Surface
